results.lead_paragraph: THE next ten years promise developments in space which were previously contemplated only in fantasy. A few short years ago a prophecy that 1959 would have brought with it not only satellites of the earth but satellites of the sun and a lunar vehicle to relay to us a picture of the hidden side of the moon would have brought unmerciful ridicule.
